# Design System: Component Patterns

> **Scope**: Applies to shadcn/ui component files. Governs how components are styled and composed.
> **Full spec**: `docs/design-system/components.md`

## Core Principles

- All components use `cva` + `tailwind-merge` via `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`
- Follow shadcn/ui New York style conventions
- Use CSS custom properties (`var(--token)`) for all colors — never hardcode hex values
- Prefer Tailwind utility classes over inline styles

## Button Contract

### Variants (CVA)

```typescript
const buttonVariants = cva(baseClasses, {
  variants: {
    variant: {
      default: "bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--accent)] to-[var(--accent-secondary)] text-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_4px_14px_rgba(0,82,255,0.25)]",
      outline: "border border-[var(--border)] bg-transparent hover:bg-[var(--muted)]",
      secondary: "bg-[var(--secondary)] text-[var(--secondary-foreground)]",
      ghost: "text-[var(--muted-foreground)] hover:text-[var(--foreground)] hover:bg-[var(--muted)]",
      destructive: "bg-[var(--destructive)] text-[var(--destructive-foreground)]",
      link: "text-[var(--accent)] underline-offset-4 hover:underline",
    },
    size: {
      sm: "h-9 px-3 text-xs rounded-lg",
      default: "h-10 px-4 text-sm rounded-xl",
      lg: "h-12 px-6 text-base rounded-xl",
      icon: "h-10 w-10 rounded-xl",
    },
  },
});
```

### Hover Behavior

- Lift: `hover:-translate-y-0.5`
- Active press: `active:scale-[0.98]`
- Transition: `transition-all duration-200`
- Arrow icons: `group-hover:translate-x-1`

## Card Contract

### Standard Card

```tsx
<Card className="rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)] shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
```

### Featured Card (Gradient Border)

```tsx
<div className="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--accent)] via-[var(--accent-secondary)] to-[var(--accent)] p-[2px]">
  <div className="h-full w-full rounded-[calc(12px-2px)] bg-[var(--card)]">
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

### Hover Effects

- Gradient overlay: `bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/[0.03] to-transparent`
- Shadow deepens: `shadow-md` → `shadow-xl`
- Icon scale: `group-hover:scale-110`

## Input Contract

- Height: `h-12` to `h-14`
- Border: `1px` in `border` color
- Border-radius: `rounded-lg` or `rounded-xl`
- Focus: `ring-2 ring-[var(--accent)] ring-offset-2`
- Placeholder: `text-[var(--muted-foreground)]/50`

## Badge / Section Label Contract

```tsx
<div className="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-[var(--accent)]/30 bg-[var(--accent)]/5 px-5 py-2">
  <span className="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]" />
  <span className="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[var(--accent)]">
    Label
  </span>
</div>
```

## Icon Container Contract

```tsx
<div className="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--accent)] to-[var(--accent-secondary)] text-white">
  <Icon className="h-6 w-6" />
</div>
```

## Accessibility

- Touch targets: minimum `44px` (`h-11` or `h-12`)
- Focus rings: `ring-2 ring-[var(--accent)] ring-offset-2`
- Color contrast: all text must meet WCAG AA
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` for continuous animations
